OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe day will be cloudy with
OL,6,Fonly the occasional bright or sunny
OL,7,Fspell. Showers will be scattered and
OL,8,Fmostly in the west at first. These
OL,9,Fshowers spread east from late morning
OL,10,Fbefore becoming less frequent towards
OL,11,Fthe evening.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FClear spells with scattered
OL,14,Fshowers at first, these mainly in the
OL,15,Fnorth. Briefly dry before becoming
OL,16,Fcloudy with rain spreading east later.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSaturday:FCloudy with rain at times.
OL,19,FThe rain will become widespread and
OL,20,Fheavy for a time from the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
